{
  "stem": "945.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It would house maybe-- it would hold maybe 10, 15 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't even remember, to be honest with you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we never had to use it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We never had to use it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The, the-- we suddenly heard, towards the end of the winter of '44, that the Russians were really advancing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we started to see the first signs of the Germans retreating.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We'd see the odd group of German soldiers simply going back, going from the front rather than to the front.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of Russian prisoners of war, which were being evacuated, also back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The feeling was we kind of sensed that the end of the occupation was near.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Partisans, partisans started being very active in the surrounding areas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Once in awhile, they'd venture into town and kill a Ukrainian authority or a Romanian authority.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They killed one of the local Ukrainian officials.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't very far from where we lived, and we heard about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole time-- the whole time we would see a partisan in chains being led by the Romanian soldiers, and we only knew what his fate was going to be.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We also heard that the local Jewish people were making contact with some of the Partisans and making arrangements that when the evacuation would happen, that perhaps they could forestall a massacre.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like when the Romanians evacuated the last authorities that the partisans would forestall or see that a massacre doesn't take place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know what kind of arrangements were, but we heard about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, indeed, after the war we found out that there had been such arrangements made, whether it would have helped or not, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
